303
00:22:59,330 --> 00:23:01,080
and have barbecue

304
00:23:05,500 --> 00:23:06,830
This year

305
00:23:08,710 --> 00:23:10,670
It's just me

306
00:23:16,460 --> 00:23:17,750
It's kind of ridiculous

307
00:23:17,750 --> 00:23:20,250
When I passed by your club today

308
00:23:20,250 --> 00:23:22,210
and saw many posters

309
00:23:23,460 --> 00:23:25,210
Then I saw you

310
00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:28,710
