317
00:24:01,380 --> 00:24:02,460
It’s okay...

318
00:24:02,460 --> 00:24:04,580
It's not absurd at all

319
00:24:05,250 --> 00:24:07,170
alright, I've decided

320
00:24:07,170 --> 00:24:11,500
Tonight, treat me as if I were him

321
00:24:11,500 --> 00:24:12,830
I'll stay with you

322
00:24:12,830 --> 00:24:15,830
