522
00:39:13,670 --> 00:39:15,540
Dear, for my sake

523
00:39:15,540 --> 00:39:17,170
have some drinks

524
00:39:17,170 --> 00:39:18,630
please

525
00:39:18,630 --> 00:39:20,290
Cheers

526
