562
00:41:12,750 --> 00:41:13,920
Leave it to me

563
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:16,420
I’ll turn them into sales kings in no time

564
00:41:18,750 --> 00:41:19,670
Remember

565
00:41:19,670 --> 00:41:22,040
