568
00:41:26,040 --> 00:41:28,130
Your expression must match your movement

569
00:41:28,130 --> 00:41:29,670
zero point

570
00:41:29,670 --> 00:41:30,460
zero point

571
00:41:30,460 --> 00:41:32,000
Pay attention to client’s strengths

572
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:33,250
